@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ernymu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.18
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.43) * v2) - wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.25)))
    v2 = 0.16
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.59) + (v2 + 0.78 + v2 + 0.34)) - (v2 / v2))
    v0 = wp.sin(0.20)
    data[tid] = v0
